The paper discusses discovering patterns and global patterns in data mining, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of a constraint-based language to model and mine patterns is also related to constraint programming (cs.CP) and database systems (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper mentions clustering, which is a common topic in data science (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE).
